  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Economics Tuition Teacher",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Axiom Education</strong><br>\nAxiom Education is a leading tuition centre for IB, A-Level (H2), Integrated Programme (IP) and O-Level. We pair rigorous, structured teaching with a fun, competitive classroom vibe. With proven materials, engaging methods and a vibrant, high-energy learning community, our students consistently climb to 7s and As.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>The Role</strong><br>\nTeach <strong>IGCSE, IB &amp; H2 Economics</strong> full-time. Run interactive, exam-focused classes and mentor students. Ideal for an educator with <strong>3–5 years</strong> of strong results.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver engaging lessons aligned to <strong>IGCSE, IB &amp; H2 Economics</strong> syllabus</li>\n  <li>Create notes, practice sets and model answers; track progress with clear, actionable feedback.</li>\n  <li>Coach exam technique: <strong>DRQ/data response</strong>, essay planning, timed practice, and marking-criteria alignment.</li>\n  <li>Provide mentorship beyond class (consults, study plans, script reviews).</li>\n  <li>Stay current with syllabus updates and exam trends.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What You Bring</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>3–5 years</strong> proven IB/H2/IGCSE <strong>Economics</strong> teaching or tutoring experience with strong outcomes.</li>\n  <li>Degree in <strong>Economics</strong> or a closely related field.</li>\n  <li>Mastery of core areas (micro, macro, international, development; for H2: market structures, elasticity, externalities, fiscal/monetary policy, balance of payments).</li>\n  <li>Clear communicator; organised, proactive, high-energy, student-centric.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Compensation (Full-Time)</strong><br>\nRevenue-share on <strong>Net Class Fees</strong> with significant upside as your classes scale.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Location</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Holland Village</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Balmoral</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Apply Now</strong><br>\nSend your resume to <strong>info@axiomeducation.sg</strong>.</p>",
